research and writing, four years, all right?

71
00:03:23,392 --> 00:03:25,193
I spent a lot of time talking to game designers,

72
00:03:25,273 --> 00:03:27,154
mainly over Skype, sometimes in person,

73
00:03:27,655 --> 00:03:30,356
and in the end I had over 100 hours of recorded interviews

74
00:03:30,516 --> 00:03:31,697
and transcription was horrible.

75
00:03:32,117 --> 00:03:34,298
This is actually gonna be a book from Focal Press

76
00:03:34,338 --> 00:03:35,919
called Why We Design Games.

77
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:37,459
It's coming out in December.

78
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,460
So the next question I had was,

79
00:03:39,781 --> 00:03:41,601
what is the best way to actually tell this story?

80
00:03:42,742 --> 00:03:42,862
Now.

